docs.title: Header 1
docs.text: This is a normal paragraph following a header. GitHub is a code hosting platform for version control and collaboration. It lets you and others work together on projects from anywhere.

docs.title: Header 2
docs.text:

When something is important enough, you do it even if the odds are not in your favor.

  return true;
}

GitHubPages::Dependencies.gems.each do |gem, version|
  s.add_dependency(gem, "= #{version}")
end
